{"tid":2210242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港版國安法｜港人在台生活困難 蔡英文:將提供最多協助","createTime":"2020-09-20T09:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T10:36:35.000Z","uid":53379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cca1c0f89f4423d37ffe94ca8d5bc9fa9815d65e","tid":2210242,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:09:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">港版國安法｜港人在台生活困難 蔡英文:將提供最多協助</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前身在台灣的銅鑼灣書店店長林榮基，前日與訪台的美國官員表示，不少到台灣尋求協助的港人生活困難，有意前往美國。對於這問題，台灣總統蔡英文今天表示，將會檢視目前典章制度的障礙，盼提供最多協助。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文今早出席公開場合時表示，香港的朋友如果有意願可到台灣工作或居住，現有的典章制度如果有障礙，當局都會一一檢視，盼提供最多協助，特別是人道協助，目前政府亦已經成立特別辦公室處理。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200920/KBYUFUCQWRD7BHAXVB6AR6D67U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1QHyonNwjet6KH6iiCOdrE5hmkMofNbwPtUY4mW8vkX23o6d19wd3XdF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200920%2FKBYUFUCQWRD7BHAXVB6AR6D67U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1QHyonNwjet6KH6iiCOdrE5hmkMofNbwPtUY4mW8vkX23o6d19wd3XdF4&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=0145cd52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200920%2FKBYUFUCQWRD7BHAXVB6AR6D67U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1QHyonNwjet6KH6iiCOdrE5hmkMofNbwPtUY4mW8vkX23o6d19wd3XdF4&h=e31ea9d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200920/KBYUFUCQWRD7BHAXVB6AR6D67U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1QHyonNwjet6KH6iiCOdrE5hmkMofNbwPtUY4mW8vkX23o6d19wd3XdF4</a>"},{"pid":"5e8c8e89ca4cc99798f5ae017255cf80f9577d8a","tid":2210242,"uid":33645,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"你要150萬投移再監察人3年生意當中又要硬性聘請整地長工加會計年報之類全部是錢。開業3年可以不蝕一半的幾乎無啦。就算你改一改規定類似英國。你可以轉用較有條件性類似bno的特別接收投資移民條件。反正去到定居生活的都是退休多或小本經營。所有生活都離不開台內消費。"},{"pid":"abf6e38877a62546ebf16742729bbd460ebd1fcb","tid":2210242,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e8c8e89ca4cc99798f5ae017255cf80f9577d8a","tid":2210242,"uid":33645,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"你要150萬投移再監察人3年生意當中又要硬性聘請整地長工加會計年報之類全部是錢。開業3年可以不蝕一半的幾乎無啦。就算你改一改規定類似英國。你可以轉用較有條件性類似bno的特別接收投資移民條件。反正去到定居生活的都是退休多或小本經營。所有生活都離不開台內消費。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"佢怕藍屍共諜 其實你唔係一定要偷渡先可以申請庇護"},{"pid":"d9ea01fbc6655001d36a6ef51595608cd8321d95","tid":2210242,"uid":65928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:00:30.000Z","msg":"English<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50e9e3a0a98bc6504edb996670ac8c7411a2665","tid":2210242,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:29:55.000Z","msg":"又係畀台灣做跳板，畀東風想移民去歐美文明國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9070c83f37352cf342c5e002c692d277204c4589","tid":2210242,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:36:35.000Z","msg":"台灣移民其實係最容易<br />\n只要你有150萬<br />\n有錢就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}